{"tid":2292190,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆連登狗屎拳賽正式誕生 摟揪俠 VS Dean 由一督狗屎贊助播出","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T05:23:07.000Z","uid":57282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b82749a0e1bb86a6c010a48cf69afc32c825c93a","tid":2292190,"uid":57282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾日天氣回暖 大家都燥底<br />\n但竟然好玩唔玩玩屎<br />\n<br />\n估唔到一督狗屎可以1001<br />\n更估唔到一督狗屎會引發一場大戰<br />\n可謂曠古爍今<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">第一屆連登狗屎拳賽 摟揪俠 VS Dean</span></span><br />\n介紹翻兩位選手先<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">摟揪俠：</span><br />\n背景：由細打交打到大 未撚驚過<br />\n有預知能力 <br />\n只用連登id 可以估計到方所在地同身份 <br />\n名言：咪撚俾我見到你 唔係我一定打撚柒你<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">Dean：</span><br />\n背景：由細到大拳擊冠軍 未撚驚過<br />\n我哋專業團隊估計 佢防禦力極高 <br />\n否則唔會周圍叫人打柒自己<br />\n名言：打柒我呀屌你老母廢柴<br />\n<br />\n為咗幫助兩位選手暢通無阻地決鬥<br />\n特登為咗你哋開呢個post 希望你哋可以留低聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n最後就係 Source 唔好淨係打個機構名 最重要係圖呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ecyd0AY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcyd0AY.png&h=ec9db084&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6E3xwHE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6E3xwHE.png&h=ec613549&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBid0A0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBid0A0.png&h=2404de58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhAG9uk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhAG9uk.png&h=85b41d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bL4EbHG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbL4EbHG.png&h=4197d962&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtcKnPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtcKnPn.png&h=135860d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtVWYnH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail